metadata.name: Dots #1
metadata.description: Dots is a visually striking and vibrant project that pays tribute to the popular 'Checks' project by Jack Butcher. The project features a large multi-colored image composed of hundreds of colorful dots, each one carefully placed to create a mesmerizing and eye-catching effect. The dots come in a variety of shades and hues, creating a dynamic and ever-changing display that is sure to captivate viewers.
